data.description:
SPACIOUS 5 large Bedrooms, 3 large Bathrooms 2 story home in Dallas. Highly sought-after Trinity Groves like new construction! 12 minutes from downtown Dallas, 10 minutes from Trinity Groves which features many restaurants, and 10 minutes from Parkland, and the medical district. 
The home features downstairs a utility, powder bath, kitchen, living room, master bedroom, and bath. On the second floor, you will find 4 bedrooms and a large bath, two storage closets, and a laundry room. Two smart door locks (Front entrance and Back yard entrance), security system with cameras. 
Check out Rodeo Goat's, and Ellen's. Hottest area TRINITY GROVES, WEST DALLAS!!!
Huge irrigated lot with plenty of room for entertaining. Private backyard enclosed by a cedar fence. 
The seller is willing to sell this house fully furnished with a full listing price offer. 
Cash, financing, assumable, Lease Option.
